tion, included in\nthe full model, against experimental data, for such a system, and we find good\nagreement. However, there seems to by a slight left/right handed braid\nasymmetry in some of the experimental results. We discuss what might be the\norigin of this small asymmetry\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2014 16:37:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Mar 2014 17:57:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-07-02"}
