y was studied, and through a\ntightness argument and a pointwise two scale convergence method the homogenized\nequation was derived.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Feb 2014 23:37:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 7 Apr 2014 18:49:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-08"}
