aints on the central engine of\nGRBs. We consider a new born millisecond pulsar with strong magnetic field as\nthe central engine. On the other hand, our results suggest that the circumburst\nenvironment of GRB 120326A is very likely a stellar wind.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2014 14:03:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
